{"id":278,"ayahs":[{"number":94,"arabic":"وَلَا تَتَّخِذُوٓا۟ أَيْمَٰنَكُمْ دَخَلًۢا بَيْنَكُمْ فَتَزِلَّ قَدَمٌۢ بَعْدَ ثُبُوتِهَا وَتَذُوقُوا۟ ٱلسُّوٓءَ بِمَا صَدَدتُّمْ عَن سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ ۖ وَلَكُمْ عَذَابٌ عَظِيمٌۭ","translation":"And do not use your oaths as a means of deceiving one another-or else [your] foot will slip after having been firm, and then you will have to taste the evil [consequences] of your having turned away from the path of God, with tremendous suffering awaiting you [in the life to come].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1995.mp3","surahId":16,"words":[{"id":69427,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এটা না","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69428,"position":2,"arabic":"تَتَّخِذُوٓا۟","translation":"তোমরা গ্রহণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69429,"position":3,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنَكُمْ","translation":"শপথগুলোকে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69430,"position":4,"arabic":"دَخَلًۢا","translation":"প্রবঞ্চনার মাধ্যম","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69431,"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنَكُمْ","translation":"মাঝে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69432,"position":6,"arabic":"فَتَزِلَّ","translation":"তাহ'লে পিছলে যাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69433,"position":7,"arabic":"قَدَمٌۢ","translation":"পা","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69434,"position":8,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69435,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُبُوتِهَا","translation":"তা স্থির হওয়ার","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69436,"position":10,"arabic":"وَتَذُوقُوا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা স্বাদ নিবে","audioUrl":"wbw/016_094_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":69437,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلسُّوٓءَ","translation":"মন্দ